The '''Tsik-Seru''' were organic vehicles used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] as atmospheric fighters.

The Tsik-Seru was a military variant of the [[Tsik vai]] and was heavily armored and equipped with [[Yaret-Kor]]s. They could survive on [[Planet/Legends|planets]] with no [[Oxygen/Legends|oxygen]] or [[Water/Legends|water]]. They were slower and less maneuverable than the Tsik-Vai since they were heavily armored.

Tsik-Seru participated in the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Coruscant]].

